About XSFun Games
Our small team in China - plus our freelancers across the globe - know that it's simple things that make a difference. So that's what we focus on when we're making our games. Get the details right, and everything else falls into place! Also - Casual Games.
What We Do
Mobiles and tablets have opened up a totally new way of playing games, and at XSFun Games, we're taking full advantage of that. With awesome touch screen controls, top-notch graphics and a lot of imagination, we're making games like no other!